# Input

```yml
{
  foo : !!str,
  !!str : bar,
}

```


# Prettier differences

```diff
--- Prettier
+++ Biome
@@ -1 +1,4 @@
-{ foo: !!str , !!str : bar }
+{
+  foo : !!str,
+  !!str : bar,
+}
\ No newline at end of file
```

# Output

```yml
{
  foo : !!str,
  !!str : bar,
}```
